          "text": "This sounds like an epic fail. I can't wait to hear @sama say his fav historical words \"We've screwed up... again. And again\".\n\nBTW, it 4o, 4.1 and other popular models return, and @openai finally change their vile overcensored policies (Anthropic is a great example of the real Ethical AI Company), maybe, OpenAI still can save their PR.\n\nHere's what they need to do. \n- Urgently bring 4o-latest back to ChatGPT AND API #BringBack4o \n- Open-source all of GPT-4 models, including all 4o snapshots, including Latest, and GPT-4.1.\n- Rename \"Legacy\" to \"Legend\" and ensure us that these models remain available for long-long-long term. \n\nWe will forgive OpenAI and Sam Altman, and @gdb and all of the rest team. \n\nAm I right, #keep4o community? Or is it better to enjoy us mass #QuitGPT and asking to #FireSamAltman ?\n#openai #ai #technology"
